{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FspXz9E2mmYC1YgUFNR1wd","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Here are the results:\n\n## 1. Search for \"swaync\" references\n\nNo matches found. The grep search returned \"No files found\" — meaning there are zero references to \"swaync\" anywhere under `/home/kiriketsuki/dots/chrysaki-ralph-ags-notification-center/ags/.config/ags/`.\n\n## 2. Bar Widget Files (all exist)\n\n### BarLeft.tsx (lines 1-55)\n```tsx\nimport app from \"ags/gtk4/app\"\nimport { Astal, Gdk } from \"ags/gtk4\"\nimport { TiledBar, type SegmentDef } from \"./TiledSegment\"\nimport { ChamferedBar, JEWEL_PALETTE } from \"./ChamferedIsland\"\nimport { Battery } from \"./Battery\"\nimport { Clock } from \"./Clock\"\nimport { ActiveWindow } from \"./ActiveWindow\"\n\nexport function BarLeft(gdkmonitor: Gdk.Monitor) {\n  const { TOP, LEFT } = Astal.WindowAnchor\n\n  const segments: readonly SegmentDef[] = [\n    {\n      widget: <Battery />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-battery\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <Clock />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-clock\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <ActiveWindow />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-active-window\",\n    },\n  ]\n\n  return (\n    <window\n      visible\n      name=\"chrysaki-bar-left\"\n      namespace=\"chrysaki-bar-left\"\n      gdkmonitor={gdkmonitor}\n      anchor={TOP | LEFT}\n      exclusivity={Astal.Exclusivity.IGNORE}\n      marginTop={0}\n      marginLeft={8}\n      application={app}\n    >\n      <ChamferedBar\n        class=\"island-left\"\n        halign={1}\n        valign={3}\n        marginTop={8}\n        marginBottom={12}\n        $={(self: any) => {\n          self.setChamfer({ tl: false, tr: false, bl: true, br: true })\n          self.setGradientColors(JEWEL_PALETTE)\n        }}\n      >\n        <TiledBar segments={segments} preset=\"zigzag\" barHeight={26} />\n      </ChamferedBar>\n    </window>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n### BarCenter.tsx (lines 1-32)\n```tsx\nimport app from \"ags/gtk4/app\"\nimport { Astal, Gdk } from \"ags/gtk4\"\nimport { ChamferedBar } from \"./ChamferedIsland\"\nimport { WorkspaceIndicator } from \"./WorkspaceIndicator\"\n\nexport function BarCenter(gdkmonitor: Gdk.Monitor) {\n  const { TOP } = Astal.WindowAnchor\n\n  return (\n    <window\n      visible\n      name=\"chrysaki-bar-center\"\n      namespace=\"chrysaki-bar-center\"\n      gdkmonitor={gdkmonitor}\n      anchor={TOP}\n      exclusivity={Astal.Exclusivity.EXCLUSIVE}\n      marginTop={8}\n      application={app}\n    >\n      <ChamferedBar\n        class=\"island-center\"\n        halign={3}\n        valign={3}\n        $={(self: any) =>\n          self.setChamfer({ tl: true, tr: true, bl: true, br: true })\n        }\n      >\n        <WorkspaceIndicator />\n      </ChamferedBar>\n    </window>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n### BarRight.tsx (lines 1-75)\n```tsx\nimport app from \"ags/gtk4/app\"\nimport { Astal, Gdk } from \"ags/gtk4\"\nimport { TiledBar, type SegmentDef } from \"./TiledSegment\"\nimport { ChamferedBar, JEWEL_PALETTE } from \"./ChamferedIsland\"\nimport { MediaPlayer } from \"./MediaPlayer\"\nimport { PulseAudio } from \"./PulseAudio\"\nimport { Network } from \"./Network\"\nimport { SystemTray } from \"./SystemTray\"\nimport { ServiceStatus } from \"./ServiceStatus\"\nimport { NotificationToggle } from \"./NotificationToggle\"\nimport { PowerMenu } from \"./PowerMenu\"\n\nexport function BarRight(gdkmonitor: Gdk.Monitor) {\n  const { TOP, RIGHT } = Astal.WindowAnchor\n\n  const segments: readonly SegmentDef[] = [\n    {\n      widget: <SystemTray />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-tray\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <MediaPlayer />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-media\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <PulseAudio />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-volume\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <Network />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-network\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <ServiceStatus />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-services\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <NotificationToggle />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-notifications\",\n    },\n    {\n      widget: <PowerMenu />,\n      cssClass: \"segment-power\",\n    },\n  ]\n\n  return (\n    <window\n      visible\n      name=\"chrysaki-bar-right\"\n      namespace=\"chrysaki-bar-right\"\n      gdkmonitor={gdkmonitor}\n      anchor={TOP | RIGHT}\n      exclusivity={Astal.Exclusivity.IGNORE}\n      marginTop={0}\n      marginRight={8}\n      application={app}\n    >\n      <ChamferedBar\n        class=\"island-right\"\n        halign={2}\n        valign={3}\n        marginTop={8}\n        marginBottom={12}\n        $={(self: any) => {\n          self.setChamfer({ tl: false, tr: false, bl: true, br: true })\n          self.setGradientColors(JEWEL_PALETTE)\n        }}\n      >\n        <TiledBar segments={segments} preset=\"zigzag-alt\" barHeight={26} />\n      </ChamferedBar>\n    </window>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n## 3. All files in ags/.config/ags/widgets/\n\n```\nActiveWindow.tsx\nBarCenter.tsx\nBarLeft.tsx\nBarRight.tsx\nBattery.tsx\nChamferedIsland.tsx\nClock.tsx\nMediaPlayer.tsx\nNetwork.tsx\nNotificationCenter.tsx\nNotificationToast.tsx\nNotificationToggle.tsx\nPowerMenu.tsx\nPulseAudio.tsx\nServiceStatus.tsx\nSystemTray.tsx\nThemeButton.tsx\nTiledSegment.tsx\nWallpaperButton.tsx\nWorkspaceIndicator.tsx\n```"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a7dfc3e1a27c87f56 (use SendMessage with to: 'a7dfc3e1a27c87f56' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 76138\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 17382</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ed3ae5d5-6d68-4c01-8434-1b6218a239c4","uuid":"5cc9c460-8382-4951-b003-176e3f0545bd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T11:54:47.972Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"In the repository at /home/kiriketsuki/dots/chrysaki-ralph-ags-notification-center, do the following:\n\n1. Search for any references to \"swaync\" in ALL files under ags/.config/ags/ (use grep/ripgrep). Report every match with file and line n